    • flightTicketList

      public static HashMap<Integer,​Ticket> flightTicketList​(int confirmationNumber, int flightID, String userName, int seatsPurchased, String seatType, double totalPrice)
      Methods that creates a map with ticket objects for employee
      Parameters:
      confirmationNumber - Ticket Number
      flightID - ID of flight tickets bought from
      userName - userName of user who bought tickets
      seatsPurchased - Number of seats purchased
      seatType - Type of seats purchased
      totalPrice - Total price of seats purchased
      Returns:
      Return hashmap of ticket objects for employees
